At the start of your first turn > You may play a Weapon onto one of your Omnibots.

Bot Mode:
When one of your Omnibots with a Weapon attacks > It gets Bold until end of battle equal to the number of Omnibots you have with a Weapon. (For example, if your character has Bold 3 when attacking, flip 3 more battle cards.)

fields.Name: Megatron
fields.Subtitle: Decepticon Leader
fields.Card Text:
Alt Mode:
When you flip to this mode > You may scrap a card from your hand. If you do, scrap an enemy Upgrade.

Bot Mode:
Pierce 3 (Do at least 3 damage when attacking, but not more than [ATK] total.)

fields.Name: Major Shockwave
fields.Subtitle: Applied Sciences • Scientist
fields.Card Text:
Alt Mode:
You may look at the top card of your deck at any time.
When you flip to this mode → Draw a card. Then your opponent chooses a card from their hand and scraps it.

Bot Mode:
You may look at the top card of your deck at any time.
While the top card of your deck is a Decepticon card or a Secret Action → You may play it as though it were in your hand.

fields.Name: Captain Elita-1
fields.Subtitle: Special Ops • Ranger
fields.Card Text:
Alt Mode:
When you flip to this mode > Move any number of damage counters from one of your other characters to this, but not enough to KO her.

Bot Mode:
When this is KO'd > Scrap the top card of your deck. You may play it. Then scrap another card from the top of your deck. You may play it.

fields.Name: Predacon Headstrong
fields.Subtitle: Ground Assault
fields.Card Text:
Alt Mode:
Brave (Enemies attack this character if able.)

fields.Name: Autobot Jazz
fields.Subtitle: Special Ops
fields.Card Text:
Alt Mode:
When this defends against an enemy that doesn't have Pierce and you flip at least ◻️◻️  → This can't take more than 2 damage this attack.

Bot Mode:
When this attacks and you flip at least ◻️◻️ → This gets Pierce 2 until after the attack.
(Do at least 2 damage when attacking, but not more than [ATK] total.)
